flowchart TD
  %% Feedback loop pattern: Multiple control loops with shared nodes
  %% Tests: back-edge detection, nested cycle handling

  %% Main forward path
  Input --> Process1
  Process1 --> Process2
  Process2 --> Process3
  Process3 --> Output

  %% Primary feedback loop
  Output --> Monitor
  Monitor --> Controller
  Controller --> Process1

  %% Secondary feedback loop (inner)
  Process2 --> Sensor
  Sensor --> Adjuster
  Adjuster --> Process1

  %% Tertiary feedback loop (nested)
  Process3 --> Validator
  Validator --> Process2

  %% Error recovery loop
  Monitor --> ErrorHandler
  ErrorHandler --> Input

  %% Cross-loop interaction
  Controller --> Sensor
  Validator --> Monitor
